#

Baked Ziti

45 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian-American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodPasta

Description

A comforting baked pasta dish with layers of ziti, marinara sauce, and melted cheese.

Ingredients

  • ziti pasta: 1 pound
  • marinara sauce: 4 cups
  • ricotta cheese: 15 ounces
  • mozzarella cheese: 2 cups shredded
  • parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup grated
  • italian seasoning: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
